[normal]2.2.[bold]&#xa0; 
[normal]The publication of Action for Roads is welcome in that it 
[normal]sets out the importance of the SRN and 
[normal]aims to define the needs of the network, linking investment over a period to the management structure required to deliver it. There is a concern that the absence of a 
[normal]N
[normal]ational 
[normal]T
[normal]ransport 
[normal]S
